---
title: "Auction Lifecycle End-to-End (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_idle: No active auction

    q_idle --> q_check_upkeep: CRE workflow triggers checkUpkeep
    q_check_upkeep --> q_idle: upkeepNeeded == false
    q_check_upkeep --> q_route_start: upkeepNeeded == true (eligible assets found)

    q_route_start --> q_perform_start: WorkflowRouter.onReport routes to performUpkeep
    q_perform_start --> q_pull_assets: feeAggregator.transferForSwap(auction, assets)
    q_pull_assets --> q_set_start: s_auctionStarts[asset] = block.timestamp
    q_set_start --> q_approve_cowswap: forceApprove(gpV2VaultRelayer, balance)
    q_approve_cowswap --> q_live: Auction is LIVE

    q_live --> q_price_push: Price manager workflow pushes streams prices
    q_price_push --> q_live: transmit() stores fresh prices

    q_live --> q_cowswap_bid: CowSwap solver calls settlement
    q_cowswap_bid --> q_validate_sig: isValidSignature validates order
    q_validate_sig --> q_cowswap_settle: order valid, vault relayer pulls asset
    q_cowswap_settle --> q_live: partial fill, auction continues

    q_live --> q_direct_bid: External bidder calls bid()
    q_direct_bid --> q_transfer_asset: asset transferred to bidder
    q_transfer_asset --> q_callback: optional callback execution
    q_callback --> q_pull_link: safeTransferFrom(bidder, auction, assetOutAmount)
    q_pull_link --> q_live: bid settled, auction continues

    q_live --> q_solver_bid: AuctionBidder.bid via WorkflowRouter
    q_solver_bid --> q_execute_swap: callback executes aggregator swap route
    q_execute_swap --> q_live: bid settled via AuctionBidder

    q_live --> q_check_end: CRE workflow triggers checkUpkeep
    q_check_end --> q_perform_end: duration elapsed OR balance below min
    q_perform_end --> q_return_remaining: remaining asset to feeAggregator
    q_return_remaining --> q_send_link: assetOut (LINK) to assetOutReceiver
    q_send_link --> q_revoke: revoke CowSwap vault relayer approval
    q_revoke --> q_idle: Auction ENDED, s_auctionStarts[asset] = 0

    note right of q_live
        INV-001: Three concurrent bidding paths (CowSwap solvers, direct bidders, AuctionBidder)
        INV-002: Price decays linearly from startingPriceMultiplier to endingPriceMultiplier
        INV-003: All bid paths enforce same price curve via _getAssetOutAmount
        INV-004: Auction can end by duration timeout OR balance below minAuctionSizeUsd
        INV-005: Remaining assets always returned to FeeAggregator on end
        INV-006: LINK proceeds always sent to assetOutReceiver on end
    end note
